{"tid":2036221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全國人大審議「港區國安法」修改稿　  據悉有數處改動","createTime":"2020-05-26T10:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T12:03:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"504fb6f913ab59299431801b3addf5f85a64af50","tid":2036221,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"全國人大下午審議常委會建立「港區國安法」和健全執行機制的決定草案修改稿，據了解，草案有數處修改。<br />\n<br />\n修改稿獲會議主席團開會通過，據了解，決定草案原本提到「禁止危害國安的行為」的相關内容，最新版本都改為「禁止危害國安的行為和活動」，增加「活動」的概念。<br />\n<br />\n至於較受爭議的第4項決定，有關<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中央維護國安的機關可能在港設立機構的内容，則沒有改動。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據議程，人大星期四早上會審議決定草案的建議表決稿，當天下午在閉幕會上進行表決。"},{"pid":"096c4627ee699ea283a6a3c880e2db48edfbf3e4","tid":2036221,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬炒"},{"pid":"69263c350140a72cecdd674b9b2c6ef849a828f3","tid":2036221,"uid":37596,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"證明國安法同送中一樣，目的都係捉人回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed19e72d9b0649d00a23194179c4649021de4707","tid":2036221,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"而家鬥左 點會有回頭路"},{"pid":"772b84831bc05880f0a3f89bfdded278debddde8","tid":2036221,"uid":262093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"幾驚佢減辣，最好越改越嚴"},{"pid":"3c327a2b0204b6813fb5a8b22fa881a39934069e","tid":2036221,"uid":60366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"望到個to